high_descs: Turn to the right, and then the left to find the green trash can.
Pick up the lettuce from inside the trash can.
Carry the lettuce, turn around and locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside. Shut the fridge and then open it to take the lettuce out. Shut the door.
Take the lettuce and turn left, to go back to the sink.
Place the lettuce on the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a head of lettuce and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go left to the green garbage can.
Pick up the lettuce that is in the garbage can.
Turn around and go to the fridge on the other side of the room.
Open the fridge and put the lettuce inside, remove the lettuce after it is cold.
Turn to the left and go to the counter where the plate is.
Put the lettuce down on the plate that is on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce on a plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left, go towards the stove
Pick up the lettuce in the green box
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the lettuce in the fridge, wait, pick up the lettuce from the fridge
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the lettuce to the right of the sink on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cool a lettuce and put it on the counter
